    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Cell Phones and Health</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>David Alexander letter on potential health risks posed by cell phones suggests that people switch to pagers (July 27 article)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>I have a solution for people concerned about the possibility of health risks posed by cell phones. Try using two-way pagers to decrease the use of cell phones. They are low power and have a better connection rate than cell phones.</p>
        <p>DAVID ALEXANDERIAN  New York</p>
      </block>
